      <td>International congress: <strong>Scientific and Technological Challenges of Musicological Source Research at International Level — 50 Years RISM</strong>.Second version of internet database of Series A/IIwith biannual updates. Provider: National Information Services Corporation (NISC USA)</td>
    </tr>
